{"tid":2007274,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"今次港父贏曬  唔會再有人敢郁佢","createTime":"2020-05-08T08:56:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T09:22:35.000Z","uid":199804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"504106fff16633c78fe966f2f327b2381c1946ae","tid":2007274,"uid":199804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T08:56:02.000Z","msg":"咁樣令我地以為佢自爆，開曬香檳之際<br />\n先叫人慢慢喺唔同po講翻係其他p牌會員自爆<br />\n我地唔止掂都掂唔到佢，仲害左一位無辜嘅會員<br />\n點解佢要一個鐘後先叫人澄清？<br />\n因為佢想比我地一個鐘希望，再立即令我地絕望<br />\n為左令人知道佢咩料甚至犧牲一個手足<br />\n再一次證明港父嘅恐怖同冷血有幾深不可測<br />\n我估今次之後應該冇人敢郁港父<br />\n真係令人顫抖。。。"},{"pid":"ef1cc8a4ed2ebe6d55bea63dc8dd14098282df84","tid":2007274,"uid":314983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T08:57:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14c9f29ef0beb4ff6e7ce0d1ee27e645ac0fddf3","tid":2007274,"uid":199804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T09:21:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f14369033f149f3f52e6e7b48bae4b85180bba0d","tid":2007274,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T09:22:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}